dc_description_s: Map shows Santiago de Cuba city center with inset diagrams of progress of November 30 revolutionary uprising. On verso: map of voyage of the Granma from Mexico to Cuba, map of movements of revolutionary uprising after disembarcation, and written history of Cuban Revolution.
dc_creator_sm: Cuba. Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, issuing body
dc_publisher_s: Habana, Cuba : Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, 1976.
